tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE assets (    asset_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,    asset_name VARCHAR(255),    asset_value DECIMAL(10,2) );
CREATE TABLE assets (asset_id INT PRIMARY KEY, asset_name VARCHAR(255), asset_value DECIMAL);
CREATE TABLE liabilities (liability_id INT PRIMARY KEY, liability_name VARCHAR(255), liability_value DECIMAL);
CREATE TABLE users (user_id INT PRIMARY KEY, user_name VARCHAR(255), user_age INT, user_email VARCHAR(255));
CREATE TABLE user_assets (user_id INT, asset_id INT, FOREIGN KEY(user_id) REFERENCES users(user_id), FOREIGN KEY(asset_id) REFERENCES assets(asset_id));
CREATE TABLE user_liabilities (user_id INT, liability_id INT, FOREIGN KEY(user_id) REFERENCES users(user_id), FOREIGN KEY(liability_id) REFERENCES liabilities(liability_id));
